videos.headline: Lock's TD pass extends Missouri's lead
videos.description: Drew Lock finds Emanuel Hall in the end zone for a 34-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Missouri pushes the lead to four scores after TD pass
videos.description: Missouri WR Emanuel Hall is able to reel in 31-yard touchdown even with defensive pass interference.

videos.headline: Missouri adds to the lead with huge 70-yard TD catch
videos.description: Missouri WR Kam Scott's first ever reception turns out to be a 70-yard TD catch from QB Drew Lock.

videos.headline: UT Martin WR wide open for 51-yard run
videos.description: UT Martin RB LaDarius Galloway runs free down the sideline for a score after short pass from QB Dresser Winn.
